WEBVTT

00:01.936 --> 00:04.169
Ohh, yeah!

00:04.171 --> 00:06.839
♪ Powerpuff girls
fighting crime ♪

00:06.841 --> 00:09.108
♪ To save the world
before bedtime ♪

00:09.110 --> 00:11.477
♪ Here's the time to shine
when you're fighting crime ♪

00:11.479 --> 00:13.512
♪ Power it up ♪
♪ Who's got the power? ♪

00:13.514 --> 00:14.980
♪ We got the power ♪

00:14.982 --> 00:17.182
♪ Breaking through the wall,
gonna do it all ♪

00:17.184 --> 00:19.385
♪ We don't quit ♪
♪ Who's got the power? ♪

00:19.387 --> 00:21.020
♪ We got the power ♪

00:21.022 --> 00:23.756
Oh! Yeah!

00:30.698 --> 00:32.231
Ugh!
I can't believe this!

00:32.233 --> 00:35.501
We haven't sold a single glass
of lemonade all day!

00:35.503 --> 00:37.336
I know this pitcher
is half full,

00:37.338 --> 00:40.806
but I'm starting to see it
as half empty.

00:40.808 --> 00:43.175
Ugh!
I don't understand!

00:43.177 --> 00:45.978
Between my business plan
and my secret ingredient,

00:45.980 --> 00:48.580
this lemonade stand
should be a huge success!

00:48.582 --> 00:50.082
[ Rumbling ]

00:50.084 --> 00:52.217
What --
What's going on?!

00:54.355 --> 00:56.855
Hey, super gal pals!

00:56.857 --> 00:59.825
Princess Morbucks?!
What are<i> you</i> doing here?!

00:59.827 --> 01:01.760
I'm building
a new water slide

01:01.762 --> 01:05.164
with my
♪ Morbucks money paver! ♪

01:07.001 --> 01:09.368
Announcer:<i> Houses go in...</i>

01:09.370 --> 01:11.403
<i> water slides come out!</i>

01:11.405 --> 01:15.040
And the best part is,
just like yours truly,

01:15.042 --> 01:18.110
it runs
on cold, hard cash.

01:18.112 --> 01:20.879
Keep shoveling,
Cash Money Krew!

01:20.881 --> 01:23.248
Let the destruction begin!

01:24.185 --> 01:27.686
Time to put your plans
on ice!

01:27.688 --> 01:30.122
[ Inhales deeply ]

01:30.791 --> 01:32.558
[ Crunching ]

01:32.560 --> 01:34.726
Ha! Guess she didn't
count on that.

01:34.728 --> 01:35.794
[ Ice cracking ]

01:35.796 --> 01:37.396
Princess: Aah!
[ Grunts ]

01:37.398 --> 01:39.231
[ Groans ]

01:39.233 --> 01:40.632
Fine!

01:40.634 --> 01:43.435
But I'll be back tomorrow
with my<i> other</i> money paver,

01:43.437 --> 01:46.772
because I'm so rich,
I can do whatever I want.

01:46.774 --> 01:49.208
Cash Money Krew,
move out.

01:49.210 --> 01:51.110
Whaaaa! Oof!

01:51.112 --> 01:54.213
Blossom: Ugh!
I can't believe that Morbucks!

01:54.215 --> 01:55.547
Dude, Bloss, relax.

01:55.549 --> 01:58.417
You can just freeze
the other money paver tomorrow.

01:58.419 --> 01:59.418
Don't you see?

01:59.420 --> 02:00.752
She's got
so much money,

02:00.754 --> 02:01.987
she'll keep coming back
again and again!

02:01.989 --> 02:03.622
We'll never be able
to stop her!

02:03.624 --> 02:05.057
[ Cellphone vibrates ]
[ Gasps ]

02:05.059 --> 02:07.726
Oh! A notification
from my stock ticker app.

02:07.728 --> 02:08.727
[ Gasps ]

02:08.729 --> 02:11.263
Morbucks' company crashed!

02:11.265 --> 02:12.831
She's gone bankrupt!

02:12.833 --> 02:15.767
Who knew water slides
wouldn't be a good investment?

02:15.769 --> 02:17.336
[ Chuckling ]
Oh, man.

02:17.338 --> 02:20.405
I wish I could see the look
on Morbucks' face right now!

02:20.407 --> 02:21.840
[ Doorbell rings ]

02:23.777 --> 02:26.578
[ Laughs ]
Dreams do come true!

02:26.580 --> 02:28.780
H-Hey, super gal pals.

02:28.782 --> 02:30.449
I was just
in the neighborhood,

02:30.451 --> 02:34.486
and I thought I'd stop by
to see my closest friends.

02:34.488 --> 02:35.621
[ Chuckles nervously ]

02:35.623 --> 02:36.755
Who?

02:36.757 --> 02:38.991
Oh, man! She means us!
[ Laughs ]

02:38.993 --> 02:43.262
Uh, anyway, I was hoping I could
stay with you girls for a bit?

02:43.264 --> 02:44.496
Where are your parents?

02:44.498 --> 02:47.099
Daddy said he needed
to lay low for a while --

02:47.101 --> 02:48.934
whatever
that means.

02:48.936 --> 02:51.603
Well, you can't stay here.
Get off our doorstep.

02:51.605 --> 02:52.604
Oh.

02:52.606 --> 02:53.605
Okay.

02:53.607 --> 02:55.507
Uh, that's okay.

02:55.509 --> 02:58.443
I'll be f-fi--

02:58.445 --> 02:59.678
No!

02:59.680 --> 03:02.281
I won't be fine!
[ Sobs ]

03:02.283 --> 03:03.849
I'm desperate!

03:03.851 --> 03:05.717
I have nothing.

03:05.719 --> 03:07.319
Nothing!

03:07.321 --> 03:08.654
[ Sobs ]

03:08.656 --> 03:12.157
The point is, losing everything
has made me realize

03:12.159 --> 03:16.028
how mean I've been
to you girls, and...

03:16.030 --> 03:17.162
[ Sighs ]

03:17.164 --> 03:18.497
...I'm sorry.

03:18.499 --> 03:19.698
[ All gasp ]

03:19.700 --> 03:23.001
Well, I said my piece.
[ Sniffles ]

03:23.003 --> 03:26.038
There's a puddle over there
that looks comfortable.

03:26.807 --> 03:28.740
Princess, wait.

03:30.311 --> 03:31.410
You can stay.

03:31.412 --> 03:32.411
What?!    What?!

03:32.413 --> 03:34.012
Really?!
You mean it?

03:34.014 --> 03:36.381
Oh! Thank you,
thank you, thank you!

03:37.718 --> 03:40.319
Take this to my room when
you get the chance, would you?

03:40.321 --> 03:41.853
Thanks.

03:41.855 --> 03:43.522
Houseboy, I'm hungry.

03:43.524 --> 03:46.425
Make me
a croque<i> madame</i> sandwich.

03:46.427 --> 03:48.093
Come on!
Chop-chop!

03:48.095 --> 03:50.696
Blossom!
What'd you get us into?!

03:50.698 --> 03:52.431
Morbucks is the worst!

03:52.433 --> 03:56.401
She's<i> always</i> been the worst,
and she'll always<i> be</i> the worst!

03:56.403 --> 03:57.869
I disagree.

03:57.871 --> 03:59.338
With a little work,

03:59.340 --> 04:02.307
I'm sure I could teach her
to be a good person.

04:03.377 --> 04:05.711
This is the worst
croque madame sandwich ever!

04:05.713 --> 04:07.012
[ Splat ]

04:07.014 --> 04:09.781
[ Groans ]
She'll never be a good person.

04:09.783 --> 04:11.883
Bloss,
give it a rest already.

04:11.885 --> 04:14.886
You've been trying to train her
for six hours.

04:14.888 --> 04:16.955
Okay, let's do this
one more time.

04:16.957 --> 04:19.024
Let's say
it's Bubbles' birthday.

04:19.026 --> 04:20.525
It is?!
Ugh!

04:20.527 --> 04:22.894
Again, Bubbles,
it's not your<i> actual</i> birthday.

04:22.896 --> 04:24.563
We're just pretending.

04:24.565 --> 04:25.430
Aww.

04:25.432 --> 04:28.367
Now, take this gift --

04:28.369 --> 04:30.102
No, no, no, no!

04:30.104 --> 04:34.206
Take the present
and give it to Bubbles.

04:34.208 --> 04:35.907
Wait.
What was that word?

04:35.909 --> 04:37.709
Guh-ive?

04:37.711 --> 04:39.077
You know -- "give."

04:39.079 --> 04:42.748
Like, how I just<i> gave</i>
that present to you.

04:42.750 --> 04:44.383
Oh, yeah.
Thanks for that.

04:44.385 --> 04:46.418
[ Grunts, giggles ]

04:46.420 --> 04:47.719
Ugh! Forget it!

04:47.721 --> 04:50.489
I don't even know
why I tried!

04:50.491 --> 04:52.157
You're so selfish!

04:52.159 --> 04:52.924
Ugh!

04:52.926 --> 04:54.993
I'll be in my room.

04:54.995 --> 04:58.330
Poor people
are so sensitive.

04:59.233 --> 05:01.767
Ugh! That Morbucks --
She's just so selfish!

05:01.769 --> 05:03.669
Uh, hey, Blossom.

05:03.671 --> 05:05.270
What are you working on?

05:05.272 --> 05:06.838
Not that you care,
but I'm just working out

05:06.840 --> 05:09.608
a few kinks to my business plan
for our lemonade stand.

05:09.610 --> 05:11.276
Ooh! Let me see.
Hey!

05:11.278 --> 05:13.278
Oh.
Here's your problem.

05:13.280 --> 05:15.480
You're spending money
all wrong.

05:15.482 --> 05:16.481
Pen me.

05:16.483 --> 05:17.482
Thanks.

05:17.484 --> 05:18.950
Mm-hmm. Hmm...

05:18.952 --> 05:21.153
And...there.

05:22.122 --> 05:25.991
Princess, this business plan
is brilliant!

05:25.993 --> 05:29.161
You got to<i> get</i> money
to get<i> money.</i>

05:29.163 --> 05:31.363
You just did me a favor.

05:31.365 --> 05:32.597
Fuh-avor?

05:32.599 --> 05:35.534
Something nice
for someone besides yourself.

05:35.536 --> 05:36.635
I did?

05:36.637 --> 05:38.770
Yeah!
I guess I did.

05:38.772 --> 05:40.305
How do you feel?

05:40.307 --> 05:41.306
Poor.

05:41.308 --> 05:42.641
But good...?

05:42.643 --> 05:46.478
Like I want to keep
doing fuh-avors and guh-iving.

05:46.480 --> 05:49.381
[ Gasps ] Is this normal?
Do I need to see a doctor?

05:49.383 --> 05:50.482
No.

05:50.484 --> 05:52.217
You're becoming nice!

05:52.219 --> 05:53.985
♪ It's nice to be nice ♪

05:53.987 --> 05:56.154
♪ It's good to be good ♪

05:56.156 --> 05:59.858
♪ Doing the things
that a good person should ♪

05:59.860 --> 06:01.660
♪ Helping a friend ♪

06:01.662 --> 06:03.328
♪ Willing to share ♪

06:03.330 --> 06:07.032
♪ Lending a hand
and showing you care ♪

06:07.034 --> 06:08.700
♪ Ba, ba, ba, ba, ba ♪

06:08.702 --> 06:12.003
♪ 'Cause when you are nice,
it makes you feel good ♪

06:12.005 --> 06:16.708
♪ 'Cause you're doing the things
that a good person should ♪

06:16.710 --> 06:18.944
[ Both laugh ]

06:21.315 --> 06:24.916
Wow. I never realized
how nice it is to be good.

06:24.918 --> 06:26.918
And it's good
to be nice.

06:26.920 --> 06:29.521
And thanks to your help,
business is booming!

06:29.523 --> 06:32.424
Your secret ingredient is
what keeps them coming back.

06:32.426 --> 06:33.525
Thanks.

06:33.527 --> 06:35.994
I spent all last summer
developing it.

06:35.996 --> 06:37.996
Hopefully, one day,
I can patent it

06:37.998 --> 06:40.265
and make
a really successful company.

06:40.267 --> 06:43.602
<i> And</i> I could use
a co-CEO.

06:43.604 --> 06:44.603
Whoo!

06:44.605 --> 06:47.072
[ Both laugh ]

06:47.074 --> 06:49.207
[ Camera clicking ] This is weird, right?
It's weird.

06:49.209 --> 06:51.376
It's like Blossom found
the last shred of decency

06:51.378 --> 06:54.613
in Morbucks' cold, dead heart
and brought it out of her.

06:54.615 --> 06:57.082
Now she's got
a<i> warm,</i> dead heart.

06:57.084 --> 06:59.584
This birthday just keeps getting
better and better!

06:59.586 --> 07:02.754
Hey, guys,
be sure to stay hydrated.

07:02.756 --> 07:03.855
Smile!

07:03.857 --> 07:04.956
Cheese.
[ Engine revs ]

07:04.958 --> 07:06.525
♪ I'm a rich boy ♪

07:06.527 --> 07:08.693
♪ Don't you wish
you had my toys? ♪

07:08.695 --> 07:10.295
My Cash Money Krew!

07:10.297 --> 07:13.932
But you're riding
with...Benny Benjamins?!

07:13.934 --> 07:15.534
[ Ka-ching! ]
♪ Rich boy ♪

07:15.536 --> 07:18.904
Buttercup: Whoa!
Are you seeing that grill?

07:18.906 --> 07:21.072
I'm burning through cash!

07:21.074 --> 07:22.908
[ Laughs ]

07:22.910 --> 07:24.309
Dang, Morbucks!

07:24.311 --> 07:27.212
You used to be hundo-P
'bout them hundo bills.

07:27.214 --> 07:29.581
Now you straight busted!

07:29.583 --> 07:30.582
[ Gasps ]

07:30.584 --> 07:32.651
None of what you just said
were words.

07:32.653 --> 07:34.820
Ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-ch-chiggity
check it, yo.

07:34.822 --> 07:36.321
Benny's a<i> real</i> friend.

07:36.323 --> 07:38.557
[ Ka-ching! ] He pays us
to hang out with him.

07:38.559 --> 07:39.758
[ Laughs ]

07:39.760 --> 07:43.261
Enjoy the simple life,
Nobucks!

07:43.263 --> 07:46.398
[ Echoing ] Nobucks!

07:46.400 --> 07:48.767
Wow. He has
an echo machine.

07:48.769 --> 07:51.002
Ha! "Nobucks" --
That's good.

07:51.004 --> 07:52.137
Wish<i> I</i> thought of that.

07:52.139 --> 07:54.439
Uh, forget them,
P-shooter.

07:54.441 --> 07:56.341
You're better
than that.

07:56.343 --> 07:58.310
Come on.
Let's go inside.

07:58.312 --> 08:00.846
Oh. Can you grab
my lockbox?

08:00.848 --> 08:02.614
Uh, sure.

08:02.616 --> 08:05.350
<i> Temptation!</i>

08:06.620 --> 08:07.619
[ Snoring ]

08:07.621 --> 08:08.954
[ Rumbling ]

08:08.956 --> 08:11.189
What's all that noise?

08:14.094 --> 08:15.794
Is that P-Shooter?

08:15.796 --> 08:19.331
I prefer
"Princess Morbucks."

08:19.333 --> 08:22.801
News flash --
I'm rich again!

08:22.803 --> 08:23.935
But how?

08:23.937 --> 08:25.604
[ Cellphone beeps, vibrates ]

08:25.606 --> 08:29.541
"Morbucks Back on Top
with New Lemonade Recipe"?

08:29.543 --> 08:31.710
<i> It's in</i>
<i> the secret ingredient.</i>

08:31.712 --> 08:34.446
<i> I spent all last summer</i>
<i> developing it.</i>

08:34.448 --> 08:37.549
That's --
That's<i> my</i> secret ingredient!

08:37.551 --> 08:39.818
[ Singsong voice ]
Not anymore!

08:39.820 --> 08:41.620
But...I don't get it.

08:41.622 --> 08:47.125
I [sniffles] I thought we were
[sniffles] were friends!

08:47.127 --> 08:49.895
[ Crying ]

08:49.897 --> 08:52.130
I thought
you were a nice person!

08:52.132 --> 08:56.835
Well, it's nice to be nice,
but it's<i> great</i> to be rich!

08:56.837 --> 08:59.037
Cash Money Krew,
show these girls

08:59.039 --> 09:01.072
the true meaning
of friendship --

09:01.074 --> 09:03.408
with violence!

09:04.711 --> 09:05.844
[ Roars ]

09:05.846 --> 09:09.014
How dare you say that
on my birthday!

09:09.016 --> 09:11.082
Rrrrrrah!

09:11.084 --> 09:13.552
[ Beatboxing ]

09:16.156 --> 09:17.155
Unh!

09:17.157 --> 09:18.857
What the --

09:18.859 --> 09:19.858
[ Ting! ]

09:19.860 --> 09:20.892
[ Laughs ]

09:20.894 --> 09:22.694
And now...

09:22.696 --> 09:23.662
[ Engine revs ]

09:23.664 --> 09:26.565
...let's get this party
started.

09:26.567 --> 09:28.433
♪ Hey, honey,
look at my money ♪

09:28.435 --> 09:30.368
♪ Look at my money,
look at my money ♪

09:30.370 --> 09:32.370
♪ Hey, honey,
look at my money ♪

09:32.372 --> 09:34.205
♪ Look at my money,
look at my money ♪

09:34.207 --> 09:36.207
♪ Hey, honey,
look at my money ♪

09:36.209 --> 09:37.742
♪ Look at my money -- ♪
[ Clears throat ]

09:37.744 --> 09:39.411
[ Music stops ] Are you
gonna move or not, B?

09:39.413 --> 09:42.914
I-I-I mean...
Loserpuff!

09:42.916 --> 09:44.616
Sure. I'll move.

09:44.618 --> 09:47.018
I just wanted
to give you this.

09:47.020 --> 09:48.954
I made it for you
last night.

09:48.956 --> 09:50.455
Ugh!

09:50.457 --> 09:53.091
Making me
go down there...

09:53.093 --> 09:56.294
Okay, what is it?!

10:00.100 --> 10:01.566
It's...

10:01.568 --> 10:03.702
It's...cheap.

10:03.704 --> 10:05.570
And it's...tacky.

10:05.572 --> 10:06.871
And I hate it.

10:06.873 --> 10:08.406
I hate it so much

10:08.408 --> 10:10.442
that I'm going to
take it home with me

10:10.444 --> 10:13.244
and laugh at it
in my giant room

10:13.246 --> 10:16.781
after I destroy
your house!

10:16.783 --> 10:18.283
[ Grunting ]

10:19.753 --> 10:22.053
You know what?
[ Scoffs ] Forget it.

10:22.055 --> 10:25.056
I don't<i> want</i> to build
a water slide here anymore.

10:25.058 --> 10:27.959
I get it --
because we're friends!

10:27.961 --> 10:32.097
No, it's because
water slides are...passé.

10:32.099 --> 10:34.899
Let's go,
Cash Money Krew!

10:34.901 --> 10:36.501
[ Roars ]

10:37.971 --> 10:39.270
Thanks, Morbucks.

10:39.272 --> 10:41.439
Don't thank me,
you nerd.

10:41.441 --> 10:43.108
[ Singsong voice ]
There's good in you!

10:43.110 --> 10:44.342
[ Singsong voice ]
No, there isn't!

10:44.344 --> 10:46.144
We're friends!

10:46.146 --> 10:47.946
No, we're not!

10:47.948 --> 10:49.447
Yes, we are!

10:49.449 --> 10:51.516
[ Normal voice ]
No! Be quiet!

10:51.518 --> 10:52.984
Bye-bye!

10:52.986 --> 10:56.321
Sorry, Bloss. Told you
you can't change a bad egg.

10:56.323 --> 10:59.324
Mm...I'm not so sure
about that, Buttercup.

10:59.326 --> 11:01.760
This was
the best birthday ever!

11:06.133 --> 11:07.599
♪ Powerpuff girls
fighting crime ♪

11:07.601 --> 11:10.135
♪ Saving the world
before bedtime ♪

11:10.137 --> 11:12.804
♪ Battling evil toe-to-toe ♪

11:12.806 --> 11:16.241
♪ Saving the day,
a Powerpuff goal ♪
